text: Jens Robert Dahlqvist (16 April 1976 - 3 February 2017), nicknamed "Strängen" and "Strings", was a Swedish guitarist and singer. He was best known as a member of the rock bands The Hellacopters, Thunder Express and Dundertåget. He was born in Uddevalla, Västra Götaland County. Dahlqvist died on 3 February 2017 at the age of 40. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Rock guitarists Category:Swedish singers
